data.description:
Introducing the perfect family oasis at 67442 Jack Crawford Road in Pearl River! This beautiful 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts charming curb appeal on a sprawling half-acre lot. As you enter the home, you’re met with a spacious living room with 10-foot ceilings. 

The beautifully updated, open-concept kitchen features granite counters and elegant white shaker cabinets with crown molding detail.  Open to the kitchen is a large dining room making entertaining a breeze.

Retreat to the primary suite, complete with an ensuite bathroom showcasing a large soaking tub, and two walk-in closets. Finally, step outside to enjoy the outdoor entertaining area with a beautifully stained, concrete covered patio and additional brick paver area and charming brick fire pit. 

Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity – schedule a showing today! **Shed does not stay**
